<% provide(:title, 'Help') %>
<h1>DPR Calculator Help</h1>


<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.6.2/css/font-awesome.min.css">
<p>This is an app useable on all mobiles, tablets and desktops that calculates the mean damage done per round in D20 RPG systems</p>
<p>The app has the following features:</p>
<ul class="fa-ul">
 <li><p><i class="fa-li fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> Calculates mean damage per round for different numbers of attacks per round with different attack bonuses, damage dice, damage bonus and critical threat ranges and multipliers</p></li>
 <li><p><i class="fa-li fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> Takes into account opponent damage reduction and critical hit immunity</p></li>
 <li><p><i class="fa-li fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> Export a table of damage per round for different opponent armour classes into an Excel spreadsheet</p></li>
 <li><p><i class="fa-li fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> Sign up to the app to save rounds using different attack methods and compare them visually in an Excel chart - see the cross over points where one method becomes better than another with changing opponent armour class!</p></li>
</ul>
</br>

